title: United Kingdom Imports of Wool Fine & Coarse Animal Hair
description: Imports of Wool, Fine & Coarse Animal Hair in the United Kingdom increased to 22.57 GBP Million in September from 21.85 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Wool, Fine & Coarse Animal Hair in the United Kingdom averaged 23.81 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 47.90 GBP Million in March of 2019 and a record low of 9.23 GBP Million in June of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Wool, Fine & Coarse Animal Hair.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
